FBIS4-36816 "drnes114_j_94020" FBIS-NES-94-114 Daily Report 13 Jun 1994 ARABIAN PENINSULA Yemen Radio Reports 10 Killed in Aden Suburb Radio Reports 10 Killed in Aden Suburb EA1306204694 Aden Democratic Republic of Yemen Radio Network in Arabic 1800 GMT 13 Jun 94 EA1306204694 Aden Democratic Republic of Yemen Radio Network in Arabic 1800 GMT 13 Jun 94 Arabic BFN [Excerpt] A responsible source in the Democratic Republic of Yemen has told the ADEN NEWS AGENCY the following: The Sanaa regime continues to violate UN Security Council Resolution No. 924 by its feverish aggression against the Democratic Republic of Yemen. It has been launching rockets since this morning against civilians and installations in the suburbs of Aden, the capital, in a hysterical and malicious manner. This led to the martyrdom of 10 persons, five of whom belonged to the same family. [passage omitted]
